Description: Implements Collective And Point Anomaly (CAPA), Multi-Variate Collective And Point Anomaly (MVCAPA), Proportion Adaptive Segment Selection (PASS), and Bayesian Abnormal Region Detector (BARD) methods for the detection of anomalies in time series data. 
